<h5 id="subject_876028">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=36cfbc428e4e74d2e72d6e446257e0fc&amp;topic=94485.msg876028#msg876028" rel="nofollow">关于fate的一些结构</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_876028'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_876028'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2017-08-30, 周三 00:14:47 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_876028_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
